        {
          "t": "p",
          "text": "Deploying AI tools in large organizations, such as Copilot, requires more than just licensing. It is imperative to go through the process of strategic planning, robust technical readiness, effective change management, and clear knowledge of practical implications to achieve maximum ROI. Our Microsoft Copilot consulting services provide a stepping stone to turn enterprise potential into quantifiable business value."
